    ch.epfl.lis.wingj

    Implements methods and objects to analyze automatically batch of experiments (e.g.
    ch.epfl.lis.wingj.expression
    Implements methods and objects to compute and represent 1D and 2D expression data.
    ch.epfl.lis.wingj.structure
    Implements methods and objects to generate structure models of biological organisms or organs.
    ch.epfl.lis.wingj.structure.drosophila.embryo
    Implements methods and objects to generate and describe structure models of Drosophila embryos.
    ch.epfl.lis.wingj.structure.drosophila.wingpouch
    Implements methods and objects to generate and describe structure models of Drosophila wing pouches.
    ch.epfl.lis.wingj.structure.geometry
    Implements methods to describe various geometrical features (segments, grids, etc.).
    ch.epfl.lis.wingj.structure.tools
    Implements tools required to generate structure models.
